description: Add front panel access to 22 different types of flash memory cardsThis 3.5-inch Front Bay Mount 22-in-1 Multimedia Card Reader allows for quick and easy access to the most popular flash card formats, from almost any desktop computer with a 3.5-inch bay opening.With support for Compact Flash (CF type I/II), Secure Digital (SD/miniSD/microSD/SDHC/SDXC), MultiMediaCard (MMC/RS-MMC/HS-MMC/MMCmobile/MMCplus/MMCmicro/HC-MMC), MemoryStick (MS/MS Duo/HS-MS/MS PRO/MS PRO Duo/MS PRO-HG Duo/MS-ROM/M2), and xD Picture cards, this reader is ready to handle the memory cards from virtually any portable device from cameras to music players.
title: StarTech.com 3.5-Inch Front Bay 22-in-1 USB 2.0 Multi Media Memory Card Reader - Black (35FCREADBK2)
